  "texts": [
    "Combined with three different sequence encoding methods, label encoding, one-hot encoding and two encoding, a total of 18 combination types are obtained (Figure 3-1B, C and D).",
    "For Cas9 and its variant sgRNA activity data sets, Sklearn toolkit was used to divide the sgRNA activity data sets according to the method of training set: test set =8:2, and the sequences in the training set and test set data were encoded according to 18 combination types to obtain 18 different training sets and test sets.",
    "Data trainingThe sequence fragments in the training set are encoded as training data, and the activity of SgRNA is used as training labels.",
    "The multi-layer perceptron algorithm is used to learn the training data and training labels, and the learning parameters in the multi-layer perceptron algorithm are set as default parameters.",
    "The maximum iteration learning rounds are set to 5000 times."
  ],
